$Path/$Pnam $Pver, $Pdat

Use: $Pnam name [options]

Add \"| tab_shuffle -l='2,1,4,3,7,8,5,6,9,10,11'\" to emulate PSI-BLAST with
query profiles

Options:

	-none
EOINPUT

